ItemDesc: Upon use, immediately regenerates <unbreak>50%</unbreak> of Max Energy for a single ally.
ItemBGDesc: Cooked food processed through multiple processes. The meat used is likely to be pork. It has been more than a hundred years since the Belobog Meat Factory launched the first red sausage, which can be described as a real national delicacy. "Red stew flavor, garlic flavor, pepper flavor... What is this strawberry flavor!?"
